DON HARRISON: No, no.

00:11:02.685 --> 00:11:04.810
I was trying to think if
I could relate that back

00:11:04.810 --> 00:11:06.202
to the original question.

00:11:06.202 --> 00:11:08.660
Do you think though,
that-- you know,

00:11:08.660 --> 00:11:11.325
there was a great
quote in the book that

00:11:11.325 --> 00:11:13.450
talked about-- it didn't
