00:55:46.700 --> 00:55:48.622
I'm one of those
people who have begun

00:55:48.622 --> 00:55:52.330
to rethink exactly where I
want the sort of parameters

00:55:52.330 --> 00:55:53.030
to be set.

00:55:53.030 --> 00:55:54.519
But on the whole,
I want somebody--

00:55:54.519 --> 00:55:56.227
I want somebody who
will have the default

00:55:56.227 --> 00:55:59.221
settings for privacy
set relatively high,

00:55:59.221 --> 00:56:01.464
