00:56:34.236 --> 00:56:35.540
It's more basic than that.

00:56:35.540 --> 00:56:38.450
You look at the
companies that make up

00:56:38.450 --> 00:56:41.850
the more dynamic part
of America, many of you

00:56:41.850 --> 00:56:44.748
