00:56:48.431 --> 00:56:50.886
And so, yes, there
are individual issues

00:56:50.886 --> 00:56:53.820
where privacy, as I
said, is one where

00:56:53.820 --> 00:56:56.750
I'm beginning to get more
interested from actually

00:56:56.750 --> 00:57:00.680
